<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3827223>
    dc:description "Fig. 15. Distribution of Kerkophorus scrobicolus sp. nov. (asterisks), Kerkophorus terrestris sp. nov. (circumpuncta), Selatodryas luteosoma gen. et sp. nov. (pentagons), S. roseosoma gen. et sp. nov. (triangles) and Sheldonia fingolandensis sp. nov. (squares). Contours at 1000 and 1500 m." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3827223/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3827249>
    dc:description "Fig. 27. Selatodryas luteosoma gen. et sp. nov., holotype, diameter 10.5 mm (NMSA W3925/T3873)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3827249/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3827251>
    dc:description "Fig. 28. Selatodryas luteosoma gen. et sp. nov., living animal, shell diameter 10.5 mm (holotype, NMSA W3925/T3873)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3827251/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3827253>
    dc:description "Fig. 29. Selatodryas luteosoma gen. et sp. nov., radula (holotype, NMSA W3925/T3873). A. Rachidian and left lateral teeth. B. Rachidian and innermost lateral teeth. C. Inner left marginal teeth. D. Outer left marginal teeth. Scale bars = 50 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3827253/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3827257>
    dc:description "Fig. 30. Selatodryas luteosoma gen. et sp. nov., genitalia and spermatophore. A. Entire genital tract. B. Flagellum. C. Penis extracted from its sheath. D. Spermatophore. A–C. Holotype (NMSA W3925/ T3873). D. Paratype (NMSA W9691/T3874)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3827257/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

